{"tid":1012402,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG]佛group加咗兩個專題群組","createTime":"2019-02-07T14:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T03:31:45.000Z","uid":159946,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09b1da9e80f90de16df77a44ec51f2e7ddb0d7de","tid":1012402,"uid":159946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"[img][img][url][url]日前<a href=\"https://t.me/hkbodhigarden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkbodhigarden&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=3f443f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkbodhigarden</a> 加咗兩個群組，南傳上座部同北傳大乘。呢個TG GP功能上相對變得比較似「大堂」，話題都更隨性自由，連結兩個新「專題」群組。<br />\n<br />\n香港本地大家最容易接觸到，或者由家人長輩得聞既佛教內容，一般都以北傳大乘佛教內容居多（例如拜菩薩，淨土念佛，唯識等等）。香港寺院亦以大乘佛教宗派居多，例如大嶼山寶蓮寺、鑽石山志蓮淨院，以至屯門青山禪院（青山寺）、元朗靈渡寺和凌雲寺「香港三大古剎」都係。<br />\n<br />\n開群組以來，有幸有南傳上座部（例如泰國緬甸既佛教，或者你以前聽過既小乘）既巴打絲打喺度。大家交流知多咗兩者歷史源流發展及異同後，決定開多咗兩個群組去方便更深入既學習同了解。<br />\n<br />\n連登都好多喺Ｕ讀宗教／中哲科目既巴絲對佛教有認識。如果你地本身對以上兩大宗派有取態，或者想進一步交流分享一下，歡迎你地加入交流分享。<br />\n<br />\n下面係兩篇喺互聯網上介紹上座部（南傳）同大乘（北傳）既文章。幾長，慎入。<br />\n<br />\n上座部佛教(Theravada) 和大乘佛教(Mahayana) 差在哪裡?<br />\n<a href=\"https://cuchunyiblog.wordpress.com/2018/02/22/chuncu│上座部佛教theravada-和大乘佛教mahayana-差在哪裡/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcuchunyiblog.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2Fchuncu%E2%94%82%E4%B8%8A%E5%BA%A7%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99theravada-%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%A7%E4%B9%98%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99mahayana-%E5%B7%AE%E5%9C%A8%E5%93%AA%E8%A3%A1%2F&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=34de2be8\" target=\"_blank\">https://cuchunyiblog.wordpress.com/2018/02/22/chuncu│上座部佛教theravada-和大乘佛教mahayana-差在哪裡/</a><br />\n<br />\n上座部與大乘佛教的分別<br />\n<a href=\"http://bemindful.weebly.com/1997824231370963328722823200562031525945303402099821029.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbemindful.weebly.com%2F1997824231370963328722823200562031525945303402099821029.html&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=e05e5a52\" target=\"_blank\">http://bemindful.weebly.com/1997824231370963328722823200562031525945303402099821029.html</a><br />\n<br />\n祝大家豬年身體健康、豬事順利！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/url][/url][/img][/img]"},{"pid":"1c1f7e84a3405181489bdbbced6faded49a7a61c","tid":1012402,"uid":228213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"合十"},{"pid":"d26034898f5bfdf5ebe64cf044a6836aa227d12b","tid":1012402,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3595a120b35104c01bd553bb70d751b12d651109","tid":1012402,"uid":39921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea7ca2d034444075a0ad5f90d3820ed88219762","tid":1012402,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"如果樓主去考DSE宗教科，有冇信心拎5**？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc3e29f39d9e26a89e9e853ae854c10ec37f0cd","tid":1012402,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}